<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Do Aliens Exist? The Honest Answer From the PURSUE Files | {{ site_name }}</title>
<meta name="description" content="The honest answer to what the Pentagon's UAP disclosure does and does not prove. {{ stats.total }} files reviewed. No spin. Cite-able.">
<link rel="canonical" href="{{ site_url }}/verdict.html">

<meta property="og:type" content="article">
<meta property="og:title" content="Do Aliens Exist? The Honest Answer.">
<meta property="og:description" content="What {{ stats.total }} declassified Pentagon UAP files actually prove and don't prove.">
<meta property="og:image" content="{{ site_url }}/og-cover.svg">
<meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
<meta name="twitter:image" content="{{ site_url }}/og-cover.svg">
